Package com.ktzvhad.rents.services.greenInvoiceServices

Interface GreenInvoiceService

All Known Implementing Classes:
GreenInvoiceServiceImpl
public interface GreenInvoiceService
The GreenInvoiceService interface provides methods to interact with the Green Invoice API. It contains methods to make API requests (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE) and retrieve the JWT token.
